{"id": 2450, "genre": 1000, "title": "是什么阻止了你在网上分享的念头？", "description": "在分享时想点“发送”，却又收回了手。（题图来自：iStock © MashaStarus）", "record_count": 16307, "comment_count": 49, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180704163703pHoZ18fOxAPG9SrM.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-07-04T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4444, "title": "是什么阻止了你在网上分享的念头？", "content": "什么阻止了你分享", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 290617, "content": "热情地分享了喜爱的作品，结果无人问津甚至被嘲笑", "image": "img/option/option/20180704135701RwDM6hLqb7tEK4fG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 290618, "content": "好心分享之后，不断有伸手党来要资源、求链接", "image": "img/option/option/20180704165936NbsoLyqezYJ6HK1x.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 290619, "content": "会被软件暴露足迹，去了啥餐馆点啥外卖好友都能看见", "image": "img/option/option/20180704170043cnEp0w3K5arfWO6M.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 290640, "content": "出于私心，看到一些有趣的观点和知识只想默默点收藏", "image": "img/option/option/20180704170527quWU0gae87AdnXjb.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 290642, "content": "发的内容并不想给所有人看，但屏蔽和分组又太麻烦", "image": "img/option/option/20180704171406oinlZHG3M8vVaAD1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 290659, "content": "一些独特有趣的观点想发但是忍住了，因为怕碰到杠精", "image": "img/option/option/20180704220209v0Oeqjipc4TKb7oW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 290644, "content": "人言可畏，比如说不发恋爱合照怕被嫌弃秀恩爱", "image": "img/option/option/20180704171636wWU8gAXhT3d7qMoz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 290645, "content": "不想被过度解读：发两句伤感歌词就被亲切关怀“是不是分手了？”", "image": "img/option/option/20180704172512mWeCY4sHIUjaRqvE.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 290685, "content": "这东西挺有趣但不符合我朋友圈的人设啊，还是不发了", "image": "img/option/option/20180704222103EBdiZLvtFw1C9mfu.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}